C Y B E R W A R E

Blades
Usage: blad


     Blades are retractable metal claws which may be used
in addition to normal weapons in combat.  Blades only work
in combat, so they must be extended in combat.  However,
they last the entire combat.  Energy is required for use
of blades.  Blade damage varies according to quality level.
Blades and bionics may be used togethor.

